This must be fate.

273
00:19:00,772 --> 00:19:02,027
Yes.

274
00:19:02,074 --> 00:19:03,762
It must be fate.

275
00:19:04,042 --> 00:19:05,443
Let's eat.

276
00:19:05,444 --> 00:19:06,765
Let's eat.

277
00:19:07,679 --> 00:19:09,701
Let's see if the food is to your liking.

278
00:19:12,818 --> 00:19:14,039
Thank you, Mrs. Jiang.

279
00:19:14,052 --> 00:19:17,275
Shaopeng told me
that you don't eat carrots, right?

280
00:19:25,197 --> 00:19:26,418
Thank you.

281
00:19:31,170 --> 00:19:32,170
Are you a kid?

282
00:19:32,171 --> 00:19:33,892
Why are you such
a picky eater at this age?

283
00:19:35,407 --> 00:19:36,340
Yes.

284
00:19:36,341 --> 00:19:38,029
Not only am I picky,

285
00:19:38,177 --> 00:19:40,131
but I'm also allergic to kiwis.

286
00:19:48,954 --> 00:19:49,941
Excuse me.

287
00:19:52,491 --> 00:19:53,545
Hello?

288
00:19:58,430 --> 00:19:59,250
Okay.

289
00:20:00,098 --> 00:20:01,999
I'm sorry.
Something happened at the company.

290
00:20:02,000 --> 00:20:03,668
I need to go back.

291
00:20:03,669 --> 00:20:04,569
So sudden?

292
00:20:04,570 --> 00:20:05,836
Mrs. Jiang, I'll be back tonight.

293
00:20:05,837 --> 00:20:08,239
- I'll keep some food for you.
- Thank you, Mrs. Jiang.

294
00:20:08,240 --> 00:20:09,728
Go now.

295
00:20:15,814 --> 00:20:16,581
I'll get going now.

296
00:20:16,582 --> 00:20:17,515
Be careful on the road.

297
00:20:17,516 --> 00:20:18,737
Okay.

298
00:20:20,285 --> 00:20:20,885
Let's eat.

299
00:20:20,886 --> 00:20:22,340
Don't let the food get cold.

300
00:21:00,092 --> 00:21:02,247
So, this is your room.

301
00:21:04,630 --> 00:21:06,151
It feels nice.

302
00:21:06,398 --> 00:21:07,619
It's very heart-warming.

303
00:21:08,200 --> 00:21:10,922
But it's a bit small.

304
00:21:15,974 --> 00:21:17,595
Can I get on?

305
00:21:43,802 --> 00:21:45,123
(What is it?)

306
00:21:45,437 --> 00:21:47,025
It smells like you.

307
00:22:59,960 --> 00:23:05,790
♪The city grooms the shadows
of the two people♪

308
00:23:05,900 --> 00:23:09,869
♪The sunset will awaken the memories♪

309
00:23:09,870 --> 00:23:15,900
♪At that moment, no names are needed♪

310
00:23:15,940 --> 00:23:21,400
♪Let the world burn to dust♪

311
00:23:21,820 --> 00:23:25,589
♪You are the only one
who can protect me♪

312
00:23:25,590 --> 00:23:30,589
♪We can decide on
our own touching story♪

313
00:23:30,590 --> 00:23:34,459
♪Nothing can replace
this soundless love♪

314
00:23:34,460 --> 00:23:38,469
♪I stop talking when I see you
running away from me every day♪

315
00:23:38,470 --> 00:23:42,239
♪I'm afraid to think about you,
I'm losing you♪

316
00:23:42,240 --> 00:23:46,469
♪I look for you from the sea of people♪

317
00:23:46,470 --> 00:23:48,109
♪I want to say I love you♪

318
00:23:48,110 --> 00:23:53,779
♪I convey my love for you
through the tips of our fingers♪

319
00:23:53,780 --> 00:23:58,319
♪I can only wait like a fool
because I can't hear anything♪

320
00:23:58,320 --> 00:24:02,519
♪I long to live in your heart♪

321
00:24:02,520 --> 00:24:05,889
♪I want to stop, I want to give up♪

322
00:24:05,890 --> 00:24:09,829
♪I want to forget how much effort
we've put into this♪

323
00:24:09,830 --> 00:24:13,939
♪I can't forget about
our promise on that day♪

324
00:24:13,940 --> 00:24:16,790
♪When I close my eyes♪

325
00:24:19,491 --> 00:24:20,879
You like Jiang Shaopeng.

326
00:24:25,564 --> 00:24:27,518
Is he why you broke your promise?

327
00:24:31,119 --> 00:24:35,543
(The moment I see love.)

328
00:24:35,591 --> 00:24:38,213
(Getting into position.)
Roll the camera.

329
00:24:38,927 --> 00:24:41,562
(You secretly ate again.)

330
00:24:41,563 --> 00:24:44,219
(You found out.)

331
00:24:45,968 --> 00:24:50,525
(The scenes in the script
are what we do every day.)

332
00:24:50,606 --> 00:24:54,796
(Their ears are so red.)
Action!

333
00:24:57,050 --> 00:24:58,930
Can I get on?
